PropertyValue.String: Reads all sales contract headers.
Reads the header data of all sales contracts in the system.
Reads the header of a specific sales contract.
Reads the header data of a specific sales contract, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number.
Reads all sales contract items.
Reads all item data of all sales contracts in the system.
Reads a specific sales contract item.
Reads the data of a specific sales contract item, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number and item number.
Reads all header-level partners.
Reads partner data from the headers of all sales contracts in the system. This includes fields such as partner function, customer, contact person, and more.
Reads a specific header-level partner.
Reads a specific header-level partner, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number and partner function.
Reads all header-level pricing elements.
Reads pricing element data from the headers of all sales contracts in the system. This includes fields such as pricing procedure counter, pricing procedure step, and more.
Reads a specific header-level pricing element.
Reads a specific header-level pricing element, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number, pricing procedure step, and pricing procedure counter.
Reads all item-level partners.
Reads partner data from all sales contract items in the system. This includes fields such as partner function, customer, contact person, and more.
Reads a specific item-level partner.
Reads a specific item-level partner, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number, item number, and partner function.
Reads all item-level pricing elements.
Reads pricing element data from the all sales contracts items in the system. This includes fields such as pricing procedure counter, pricing procedure step, and more.
Reads a specific item-level pricing element.
Reads a specific item-level pricing element, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number, item number, pricing procedure step, and pricing procedure counter.
Reads all header-level texts.
Reads text data from the headers of all sales contracts in the system. This includes fields such as language code, long text ID, and more.
Reads a specific header-level text.
Reads a specific header-level text, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number, language code, and long text ID.
Reads all item-level texts.
Reads text data from all sales contract items in the system. This includes fields such as language code, long text ID, and more.
Reads a specific item-level text.
Reads a specific item-level text, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number, item number, language code, and long text ID.

Creates the data of partners with a specific partner function from the header of a specific sales contract. Consumers must pass the following key fields: sales contract ID and partner function.

Deletes a specific header-level pricing element.
Deletes a specific header-level pricing element, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number, pricing procedure step, and pricing procedure counter.

Updates a specific header-level pricing element, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number, item number, pricing procedure step, and pricing procedure counter.

Deletes a specific item-level text, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number, item number, language code, and long text ID.

Creates item data for a specific sales contract, which the consumer specifies by passing the sales contract number. The consumer must also pass the sales contract number in the payload.
